'''2-硝基咪唑'''是一种有机化合物，为{{ld|硝基咪唑|Nitroimidazole}}的[[同分异构体|同分异构体]]之一，化学式为C<sub>3</sub>H<sub>3</sub>N<sub>3</sub>O<sub>2</sub>。它可以[[2-溴咪唑|2-溴咪唑]]或[[2-氨基咪唑|2-氨基咪唑]]为原料制得。<ref>吴义杰, 朱勤. [https://www.ixueshu.com/document/06485765589efeef318947a18e7f9386.html 2-硝基咪唑的制备]. 中国医药工业杂志, 1994, 025(004):181-181.</ref><ref>熊绪杰. 2-硝基咪唑的制备方法. 2020. CN 111018788 A.</ref>它可以和[[氢氧化钾|氢氧化钾]]反应，生成2-硝基咪唑钾。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Inorganic Chemistry|volume=54|issue=10|language=en|issn=0020-1669|date=2015-05-18|pages=4953–4965|doi=10.1021/acs.inorgchem.5b00554|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/acs.inorgchem.5b00554|title=Nitroimidazole-Containing H 2 dedpa and H 2 CHX dedpa Derivatives as Potential PET Imaging Agents of Hypoxia with 68 Ga|accessdate=2020-11-18|author=Caterina F. Ramogida, Jinhe Pan, Cara L. Ferreira, Brian O. Patrick, Karla Rebullar, Donald T. T. Yapp, Kuo-Shyan Lin, Michael J. Adam, Chris Orvig}}</ref>它和[[N-溴代丁二酰亚胺|''N''-溴代丁二酰亚胺]]在[[N,N-二甲基甲酰胺|DMF]]中反应，可以得到4,5-二溴-2-硝基咪唑。<ref>Palmer, Brian D.; Denny, William A. Synthesis and reactions of brominated 2-​nitroimidazoles. ''Journal of the Chemical Society, Perkin Transactions 1:  Organic and Bio-Organic Chemistry (1972-1999)'', 1989. 1: 95-99. ISSN: 0300-922X.</ref>

